    "title": "Process Engineer Vacancy at Emami Digital Technologies - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Process Engineer with drive and ambition, Emami Digital Technologies in Pune is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Emami Digital Technologies:\nEmami Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Emami Digital Technologies!",
